I JUST REALIZED THAT.

242
00:20:19,250 --> 00:20:21,083
- YOU'RE SERIOUSLY GONNA QUIT?

243
00:20:21,166 --> 00:20:24,291
- YOU SAID WE'VE ALWAYS BEEN
